★ ★ ★ ★ ★

My experience with Park+ for fastag purchase was excellent. Fastag was delivered within 5 working days after the purchase. Activation was successful with ₹99 as initial balance. I recharged my fastag with ₹500 and it was successfully completed! Park+ your services are excellent in Delhi NCR and Mumbai.

Hema Rastogi

★ ★ ★ ★ ★

It's a great app for my car needs. I had first used this app back in 2019 to book a parking slot for around Subhash Nagar. I then started exploring other features of the app and it is quite useful. I use it for my FASTag recharge regularly now. I even got my vaccine second dose because of the vaccination camps you organised. Truly a life altering app!

Resham Beri

★ ★ ★ ★ ★

With the help of the Park+ app, I came to know that my vehicle was challaned on 25 Aug. Due to COVID I was away from the city and came to Delhi only for a short trip. On my way back home I got a ticket for over-speeding. I was able to quickly check this on the app and pay the due amount without any hassle. Thank you Park+ for this application.

Sanjay Mahajan

★ ★ ★ ★ ★

I tried Park+ car wash services and have been a fan of it ever since. Regular car cleaning had become a huge challenge. Someone in my society told me about the Park+ car wash service and now I am never going back. It's quick and everything happens on the app, super easily and swiftly. I am a subscriber of this service for life now.

Prashant Rai
